br><br>The Thex Mallet was some kind of Family weapon for the King and Queen.<br><br>Whatever happened to kick Takahiz's arse and cause all of the Undead to take over must of taken the Mallet and broke it apart in Three pieces. <br><br>Two pieces to Elf Skeletons, and one piece to Cdr Windstream.<br><br>More about the King and Queen:<br><br>They are on opposing Factions. I don't know why they do not like eachother, but its pretty apparent they do not.<br><br>Right now, the King controls Neriak, and the Queen is out sleeping on the Couch. She controls the Nercomantic factions, such as Nercos, ShadowKnights, and Rouges. (Lodge of the Dead).<br><br>Where as the King is more with the Clerical and Warriors.<br><br>The Spurned (Wizards, Mages, Enchanters) are just odd.<br><br>That is all, back to FV I go just felt a need to drop some RPing knowledge on a PowerGaming Server, and I saw Taurus's name so I had to say Hi and @#%$. TaTa.<br> <p><IMG SRC="http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Shintou.gif">Shintou Shinai, <a href="http://members.tripod.com/selquar/">House Sel'quar</a>"By Hate and Rage I shine, Banegrivm, I'll burn your soul."</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/uroninsenshi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RoninSenshi</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Kanji.jpg" BORDER=0> at: 11/27/01 6:42:36 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f7f7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/utaurusl.showPublicProfile?language=EN>TaurusL</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Scowling Poster</span><br> <font color=#778899>(11/27/01 7:22:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/finnoruukserverfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_lightbulb.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Thex the name</span><hr size=